  Chit 1 kang si7 Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 in tiuN7-lang5 cho3 60 hoe3 toa7-siu7. In bou2 chhoan5 mi7-soaN3, ah-a2, chiu2 kap 1-te3 ang5-pou3 hou7 i koe3 in tiuN7-lang5 tau chiok-siu7. I beh chhut-mng5 e5 si5, in khan--e5 kau-tai3 i kong2, “Li2 seng khi3 ka7 pa-pa chiok-siu7, goa2 u7 tai7-chi3, beh-am3-a2 chiah koe3--khi3.” 
  Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 ian5-lou7 kiaN5 ian5-lou7 sng2. KiaN5 kau3 poaN3-lou7 e5 si5, ah-a2 soa3 koaN7-koaN7-koaN7 kio3 boe7 theng5. Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 sim-lai7 siuN7 kong2, “Ah, ah-a2 teh chhui3-ta--lah. Pang3 li2 khi3 chiah8 chui2.” 
  Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 siuN7 boe7 kau3 ah-a2 soa3 ju2 siu5 ju2 hng7. “Ah-a2, ah-a2, li2 phaiN2 sim-koaN, pang3 goa2 1-e5 ti7 ho5-hoaN7, lin2-pe7 iong7 mi7-soaN3 ka7 li2 phah, na7 hou7 goa2 liah8--tioh8 phah kah hou7 li2 hoah m7-kaN2.” I tioh8 iong7 chhiu2--nih8 e5 mi7-soaN3 beh lai5 khian chui2--nih8 e5 ah-a2. Mi7-soaN3 loh8-chui2 tioh8 tam5--khi3. Ah-a2 m7-na7 khian bo5--tioh8, mi7-soaN3 ma7 tam5-kou5-kou5, noa7-liau2-liau2. 
  Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 ti7 teh-beh kiaN5 kau3 in tiuN7-lang5 tau mng5-kha-khau2 e5 si5-chun7, keng-koe3 1-phiN3 tek-a2-na5. Hong chhoe-tioh8 tek-a2, hoat chhut sih-sih-suh-suh e5 siaN-im. Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 m7-kam tek-a2 teh hoah koaN5. I tioh8 theh8 sim-koaN-thau5 hit-te3 ang5-pou3 pak8 ti7 tek-a2 e5 sin-khu teng2. 
  Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 kiaN5 lai5 kau3 in tiuN7-lang5 tau e5 tiu7-tiaN5, khoaN3 tioh8 thou5-kha u7 pit-sun5. “Goa2 chai--lah, li2 e7 joah8 houNh. Lai5--lah, chit-koan3 chiu2 chhiaN2--li2.” Tioh8 an2-ne Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 siang-chhiu2 khang-khang lai5 kau3 in tiuN7-lang5 tau. 
  Am3-thau5-a2 chiah8-toh e5 si5, in bou2 khoaN3 i phaiN2-se3 ngoeh chhai3, tioh8 ti7 i e5 saN-kun5-a2-piN kat 1-tiau5 soh-a2, in bou2 tiuh 1-e7, i tioh8 ngoeh 1-e7. Ho2-si2 m7-si2 soh-a2 khi3 hou7 1-chiah koe-a2 tiN5--tioh8. Gong7-kiaN2-sai3 tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 koe-a2 chhiak8-chhiak8-thiau3 kang7-khoan2, chhiN-chham2 ngoeh, chhiN-chham2 chiah8. 
  In ang-a2-bou2 tng2 lai5 chhu3--nih8 e5 si5, soa3 lai5 khi2 phui3-bin7. I in3 in bou2 kong2, “TiuN7-lang5 in tau si7 tang-peng5 ui5 leng5, sai-peng5 ui5 hou2, au7-mng5 1 phoa3-kou2, li2 na7 khi3 khoaN3, li2 tioh8 chai goa2 khou2.」Goan7-lai5 gong7-kiaN2-sai3 chiah8 phaiN2 pak-tou2 koh chhoe7 bo5 pian7-sou2. 
  Chit-e5 kou3-su7 si7 goan2 goa7-ma2 ti7 goa2 kok-hau7 4-ni5 e5 si5 ka7 goa2 kong2--e5. Goa7-ma2 bat kong2 chin choe7 gin2-a2-kou2. Sng3--lai5 ma7 u7 10-ni5--ah, m7-ku2 goa2 iu5-goan5 ki3 chiok chheng-chho2. Oan5-choan5 long2 ai3 kam2-sia7 kok-hau7 e5 lau7-su. Na7 m7-si7 i hoat8 goa2 sau3 pian7-sou2, goa2 ma7 boe7 u7 hiah-nih8 ho2 e5 ki3-ti5 khi3 ki3 chit-e5 kou3-su7. Tioh8 in-ui7 goa2 ti7 hak8-hau7『說話課』e5 si5 iong7 goan2 ma-ma ka3--goa2 e5 gi2-gian5 lai5 kong2 goan2 goa7-ma2 kong2 e5 kou3-su7, siuN7 boe7 kau3 ti7 1991-ni5 koh u7 m7-chun2 hak8-seng kong2 in e5 bu2-gi2 e5 lau7-su. Chin ka-chai3 kau3-iok8 u7 pian3 ho2, chiah boe7 koh hai7 tioh8 kho2-lian5 e5 hak8-seng gin2-a2. 
  (Tai5-oan5-ji7 chap8-chi3 te7 15 ki5, 2003 ni5 3 geh8) 
